OL,3,CThames Water defends #1.4bn Abingdon
OL,4,Creservoir proposal
OL,6,FThames Water says a reservoir 'the
OL,7,Fsize of Gatwick airport' which would
OL,8,Fbe constructed in the Oxfordshire
OL,9,Fcountryside would benefit local
OL,10,Fresidents.
OL,12,FThe water firm is working with
OL,13,FAffinity Water and Southern Water on
OL,14,Fthe project near Abingdon, which would
OL,15,Fbe on on six square miles of land
OL,16,Fbetween Drayton and East Hanney.
OL,18,FIt will mostly supply water to people
OL,19,Fin London and the South East, one of
OL,20,Fseveral reservoirs planned across the
OL,21,Fcountry to help tackle climate change.
