OL,3,CThames Water defends #1.4bn Abingdon
OL,4,Creservoir proposal
OL,6,FIts overall aim is to help the wider
OL,7,Fregion during droughts.
OL,9,FIf the plans do go through,
OL,10,Fconstruction will begin in 2029 -
OL,11,Falmost 40 years after the initial idea
OL,12,Fwas first floated.
OL,14,FA series of events for residents
OL,15,Fliving nearby began on Thursday (27
OL,16,FJune) in Sutton Courtenay as a public
OL,17,Fconsultation starts.
