OL,3,CThames Water defends #1.4bn Abingdon
OL,4,Creservoir proposal
OL,6,FThames Water hope the use of virtual
OL,7,Freality (VR) would help alleviate any
OL,8,Fconcerns from locals so they can
OL,9,Fexperience what the project look like
OL,10,Fwhen completed.
OL,12,FThe controversial project has come
OL,13,Funder heavy scrutiny because work
OL,14,Fwould last a decade and not enough
OL,15,Fsupply would go to the surrounding
OL,16,Fareas.
