OL,3,CThames Water defends #1.4bn Abingdon
OL,4,Creservoir proposal
OL,6,F"We're absolutely delighted with the
OL,7,Flevel of response we've already
OL,8,Freceived to our public consultation,"
OL,9,Fsaid Dubois.
OL,11,F"Local communities are certainly alive
OL,12,Fto the climate change challenge and
OL,13,Frecognise that we need to invest in
OL,14,Fmore new reservoirs to support future
OL,15,Fgrowth.
OL,17,F"Naturally, we've heard from people
OL,18,Fwith concerns too, and I'd encourage
OL,19,Fthem to come and see us when we visit
OL,20,Ftowns and villages in Oxfordshire over
OL,21,Fthe next four weeks.
